' ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
' 4A. BOSS BATTLE (Major Exam/Midterm/Final) - HIGH XP
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@startuml EduMind_Sequence_BossBattle

skinparam backgroundColor #1a1a2e
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #16213e
    ParticipantBorderColor #0f3460
    ParticipantFontColor #ffffff
    ActorBackgroundColor #e94560
    ArrowColor #e74c3c
    NoteBorderColor #f39c12
    NoteBackgroundColor #2c3e50
}

title 👹 BOSS BATTLE - Major Exam (150-500 XP)

actor Student as S
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "API Server" as API
database "Database" as DB
participant "Gamification\nService" as GM
participant "Achievement\nChecker" as AC

note over S,AC #8B0000
    **BOSS BATTLE** = Major exams only
    • Midterm Exam
    • Final Exam  
    • Chapter Test
    • Competition
    
    XP: 150-500 (based on score)
    Special achievements available
    Defeat required to "clear" the chapter
end note

S -> UI: Open Boss Battle
activate UI

UI -> API: GET /quizzes/{id}/start?type=BOSS
activate API

API -> DB: Get boss battle data
DB --> API: Boss quiz (harder questions)

API -> DB: Create attempt\n(boss_battle: true)
DB --> API: Attempt ID

API --> UI: Boss data + epic UI flag
deactivate API

UI --> S: 👹 **BOSS BATTLE START**\nEpic animation + music
deactivate UI

note over S,UI #2c3e50
    Student completes boss battle
    • Time pressure
    • No hints allowed
    • All questions required
end note

S -> UI: Submit boss battle
activate UI

UI -> API: POST /boss-battles/{attemptId}/submit
activate API

API -> API: Calculate score

alt Score >= 60% (BOSS DEFEATED!)
    API -> GM: Boss defeated!
    activate GM
    
    GM -> DB: Award BOSS XP\n(150-500 based on score)
    
    note right of GM #228B22
        **Boss XP Calculation:**
        Base: 150 XP
        + Perfect (100%): +200 XP
        + First try: +50 XP
        + Speed bonus: +50 XP
        + No hints: +50 XP
        ────────────────
        Max: 500 XP
    end note
    
    GM -> DB: Mark chapter as "cleared"
    GM --> API: Boss defeated event
    deactivate GM
    
    API -> AC: Check BOSS achievements
    activate AC
    
    AC -> AC: Check conditions:\n• First Boss Defeat\n• Perfect Boss Kill\n• Speed Run Boss\n• No Damage (100%)
    
    opt Achievement unlocked
        AC -> DB: Unlock achievement\n(Boss Slayer, etc.)
        AC -> DB: Award bonus XP (200-500)
        AC --> API: Achievement data
    end
    deactivate AC
    
    API --> UI: 🎉 BOSS DEFEATED!\n+ XP + achievements
    UI --> S: Victory screen!\nEpic celebration animation
    
else Score < 60% (BOSS NOT DEFEATED)
    API -> GM: Boss attempt failed
    GM -> DB: Award consolation XP (50)
    GM --> API: Try again
    
    API --> UI: Boss not defeated
    UI --> S: "The boss is too strong!\nTrain more and try again"
end

deactivate API
deactivate UI

@enduml


